\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [C2.1]\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94Explain it to me then.\u8221\'94 You say. Rasputin nods, satisfied and motions for you to follow him. You follow.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [C2.2]\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94Everyone has to work. It\u8217\'92s the only way to keep the Bioforms out of the city. You need to stop this.\u8221\'94 You say}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 [C2.3]You look at Eve. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Please, come back home. You shouldn\u8217\'92t be doing this no matter what fucked up reasons they\u8217\'92ve given you to make you think it\u8217\'92s OK.\u8221\'94}
